"To implement the **Shopping Cart** page with the required elements and functionality based on the provided data and IDs, here is a detailed outline and example code snippets in HTML and JavaScript that you can adapt for your web application:

---

## Shopping Cart Page Overview

### Key Elements and IDs:
- **Container**: `cart-items-table` — displays the list of items in the cart.
- **Buttons**:
  - `remove-item-button-{item_id}` — removes an item from the cart.
  - `update-quantity-{item_id}` — updates the quantity of a specific item.
  - `proceed-checkout-button` — proceeds to the checkout page.
- **Inputs**:
  - `quantity-input-{item_id}` — input field for item quantity.
- **Display Fields**:
  - Item Code, Name, Description, Price, Quantity, Subtotal.
- **Data Source**:
  - Cart data from `cart.txt` or backend API.
  - Menu item details from `menus.txt`.
- **Functionality**:
  - Display all cart items with details.
  - Allow quantity update with validation.
  - Remove items from cart.
  - Show subtotal and total amount.
  - Proceed to checkout.

---

## Example HTML Structure

```html
<div id="cart-container">
  <h1>Shopping Cart</h1>
  <table id="cart-items-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Item Code</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Description</th>
        <th>Price</th>
        <th>Quantity</th>
        <th>Subtotal</th>
        <th>Actions</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody id="cart-items-body">
      <!-- Cart items will be dynamically inserted here -->
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <div id="cart-summary">
    <strong>Total: $<span id="cart-total">0.00</span></strong>
  </div>
  <button id="proceed-checkout-button">Proceed to Checkout</button>
</div>
```

---

## Example JavaScript Logic

```javascript
// Sample data format for cart items (normally fetched from backend or local storage)
const cartItems = [
  {
    item_id: 1,
    item_code: "RICE01",
    name: "Steamed Rice",
    description: "Plain steamed rice",
    price: 2.99,
    quantity: 2
  },
  {
    item_id: 2,
    item_code: "PASTA02",
    name: "Spaghetti Carbonara",
    description: "Classic pasta with creamy sauce",
    price: 12.99,
    quantity: 1
  }
];

// Function to render cart items in the table
function renderCartItems() {
  const tbody = document.getElementById('cart-items-body');
  tbody.innerHTML = ''; // Clear existing rows

  let total = 0;

  cartItems.forEach(item => {
    const subtotal = item.price * item.quantity;
    total += subtotal;

    const tr = document.createElement('tr');

    tr.innerHTML = `
      <td>${item.item_code}</td>
      <td>${item.name}</td>
      <td>${item.description}</td>
      <td>$${item.price.toFixed(2)}</td>
      <td>
        <input type="number" id="quantity-input-${item.item_id}" min="1" value="${item.quantity}" style="width: 60px;">
        <button id="update-quantity-${item.item_id}">Update</button>
      </td>
      <td>$${subtotal.toFixed(2)}</td>
      <td>
        <button id="remove-item-button-${item.item_id}">Remove</button>
      </td>
    `;

    tbody.appendChild(tr);

    // Add event listeners for update and remove buttons
    document.getElementById(`update-quantity-${item.item_id}`).addEventListener('click', () => updateQuantity(item.item_id));
    document.getElementById(`remove-item-button-${item.item_id}`).addEventListener('click', () => removeItem(item.item_id));
  });

  document.getElementById('cart-total').textContent = total.toFixed(2);
}

// Function to update quantity of an item
function updateQuantity(item_id) {
  const input = document.getElementById(`quantity-input-${item_id}`);
  const newQuantity = parseInt(input.value);

  if (isNaN(newQuantity) || newQuantity < 1) {
    alert('Please enter a valid quantity (1 or more).');
    input.value = 1;
    return;
  }

  const item = cartItems.find(i => i.item_id === item_id);
  if (item) {
    item.quantity = newQuantity;
    renderCartItems();
  }
}

// Function to remove an item from the cart
function removeItem(item_id) {
  const index = cartItems.findIndex(i => i.item_id === item_id);
  if (index !== -1) {
    cartItems.splice(index, 1);
    renderCartItems();
  }
}

// Event listener for proceed to checkout button
document.getElementById('proceed-checkout-button').addEventListener('click', () => {
  if (cartItems.length === 0) {
    alert('Your cart is empty.');
    return;
  }
  // Redirect to checkout page or trigger checkout process
  window.location.href = '/checkout-page'; // Adjust URL as needed
});

// Initial render
renderCartItems();
```

